title: Sevilla 3-3 Real Madrid (agg. 3-6): Benzema strikes late to set new record
text:
Sevilla 3-3 Real Madrid (agg. 3-6): Benzema strikes late to set new record Getty Images 0 13-Jan-2017 03:37:44 
A valiant effort from Sevilla pushed Real Madrid to the wire in a classic Copa del Rey clash, but it was not enough as Karim Benzema brought up 40 successive unbeaten games with a late strike to mark a 3-3 draw on the night.
